title: Metal Gear Solid PS1 PSN Classic for PS3 CFW 3.55 4.21+
description:
Classic game, sadly missing from the Legacy Collection. So here it is! 

Already fixed, so just install and play!

Metal Gear Solid (commonly abbreviated as MGS) is an action-adventure stealth video game directed by Hideo Kojima. The game was developed by Konami Computer Entertainment Japan and first published by Konami in 1998 for the PlayStation video game console. It is the sequel to Kojima's MSX2 computer game Metal Gear 2: Solid Snake.
